        "Description": "Good afternoon agent,\r\rThe ICA has put out a most wanted list as an incentivising challenge for all of our operatives, we want our best and brightest to impress us with a show of smarts, speed and ingenuity.\rYour targets can be handled in any way you see fit. \rYou can enter, exfil and smuggle anything within your means to mission.\rStandard ICA protocol is expected from everyone who participates so only the target is to be eliminated and there can be no evidence you were ever there.\r\rGood Luck.",
